\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 2. T. marginifolius} Pawl., {\i Bull. Soc. Nat. Moscou} nov. ser., {\b 47}({\b 2}): 83 (1938). Like {\b 1} but leaves with a white, usually coriaceous margin; achenes deeply sulcate; beak 0·6 cm, abruptly widened into body.{\i  Rocky slopes and semi-deserts. S.E. Russia.} Rs (E). ({\i C. Asia}.)
