\pard\f0\fs28    {\b 3. T. cretaceus} S. Nikitin,{\i  Not. Syst.} ({\i Leningrad}){\b  7}: 264 (1937). Like {\b 1} but biennial; stems glabrous; leaves linear; involucral bracts 8-12, somewhat exceeding ligules; beak of achene about as long as body; pappus distinctly shorter than achene. {\i Chalky slopes. • S.E. Russia} ({\i near Vol'sk}). Rs (E).
